HEADWORD: Villager
<hw>Vil"la*ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An inhabitant of a
village.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Brutus had rather be a <qex>villager</qex>⟦br⟧
Than to repute himself a son of Rome⟦br⟧
